*Dobu* je odredio njegov otac. (His father determined the time.)

*Dobom* smo odmah otputovali. (We immediately set off at that time.)

Krajnje *dobe* smo dočekali sa radošću. (We welcomed the end of the time with joy.)

U tom *dobu*, deca su bila razmažena. (At that time, children were spoiled.)

U narednom *dobu*, svi smo se osećali srećno. (In the next time, we all felt happy.)